        <abstract>
            <p>Asks for any authentic cases of "sports", which CD calls "bud-variations". Flowers introduced from warmer temperate regions are said to be particularly apt to sport in this way.</p> 
<p>CD now has proof that <hi rend="italic">Cinchona</hi> is dimorphic and that some dimorphic plants are absolutely sterile with their own-form pollen.</p> 
            <p>Asks GHKT to examine or send pollen specimens of two Ceylon genera.</p>
        </abstract>
